|               |                                         HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Inner, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(o_orderkey@1, l_orderkey@0)], projection=[c_nationkey@0, l_suppkey@3, l_extendedprice@4, l_discount@5]                                                                                                                                                                                                        |
